WEBVTT

00:49.174 --> 00:50.550
Do you really think it'll be okay?

00:50.759 --> 00:52.886
Of course. I can put on a great act.

00:52.969 --> 00:54.471
I'm confident that they won't find out.

00:55.305 --> 00:57.640
EPISODE 6

01:01.811 --> 01:03.188
The door is opening.

01:23.708 --> 01:24.834
Dad.

01:26.961 --> 01:28.838
Did you go out to exercise?

01:32.425 --> 01:33.426
Yes.

01:39.349 --> 01:40.391
Jin-a.

01:42.936 --> 01:44.729
I want you to...

01:53.238 --> 01:55.031
I lied.

02:06.334 --> 02:07.710
Is it something

02:12.799 --> 02:14.467
that can make me disappointed in you?

02:19.514 --> 02:20.473
Yes.

02:30.525 --> 02:32.652
But maybe it won't.

02:35.947 --> 02:38.408
I'll do my best
so that you won't be disappointed.

02:40.451 --> 02:41.494
And that's why

02:42.704 --> 02:44.956
I can't tell you anything right now.

02:50.336 --> 02:52.297
Please give me a little bit of time.

02:53.339 --> 02:55.341
I'll tell you everything later on.

02:57.844 --> 02:59.470
Just until then,

03:01.639 --> 03:03.349
please trust me and wait.

03:09.397 --> 03:10.565
Are you mad at me?

03:12.150 --> 03:13.484
Why would I be?

03:15.111 --> 03:17.155
Why are you staring at the floor
like that?

03:27.415 --> 03:28.917
What are you two doing?

03:29.792 --> 03:33.087
Do you have to get all pouty just because
I asked you to go exercise with me?

03:34.088 --> 03:35.715
You don't look after your health,

03:35.798 --> 03:37.342
so I suggested it for your own sake.

03:38.218 --> 03:39.928
Don't you know that I care about you?

03:40.011 --> 03:41.596
Why are you even worried about that?

03:41.679 --> 03:43.681
She's still young,
and she can take care of herself.

03:44.182 --> 03:46.267
Why are you bothering her on her day off?

03:46.351 --> 03:48.436
Stop being ridiculous and get out. Go on.

03:49.145 --> 03:52.565
Goodness, what's with him today?
He's never done that before.

03:53.441 --> 03:54.859
Why do you look so upset?

03:55.318 --> 03:58.529
My gosh, did you get changed
to go with him?

03:59.864 --> 04:01.199
I'll go with him.

04:01.574 --> 04:04.869
You don't have to force yourself
to go with him.

04:32.438 --> 04:33.773
Go!

04:36.317 --> 04:37.735
Just go!

04:39.862 --> 04:41.114
Go.

05:42.967 --> 05:44.093
Wait up!

05:48.097 --> 05:49.640
Have we been out for long enough?

05:52.060 --> 05:53.269
Yes, I think so.

05:55.021 --> 05:56.481
Let's head back home, then.

05:58.316 --> 05:59.400
Dad.

06:21.756 --> 06:23.549
Why do you keep saying you're okay?

06:25.259 --> 06:26.511
What did he say?

06:30.056 --> 06:31.974
I don't want you to stress over it
all alone.

06:34.310 --> 06:35.937
He really didn't say anything.

06:36.479 --> 06:39.273
Frankly, getting yelled at
would've been much better.

06:40.441 --> 06:42.735
I shouldn't have asked you to stay
last night.

06:44.904 --> 06:47.657
It's not like you forced me to stay.

06:48.282 --> 06:50.451
I stayed because I wanted to.

06:51.619 --> 06:53.412
You don't have to try
to make me feel better.

06:54.413 --> 06:57.959
I'm not trying to make you feel better.
I'm just telling you the truth.

07:01.045 --> 07:02.130
You're pretty.

07:03.506 --> 07:04.841
I told you I already know that.

07:07.593 --> 07:09.303
When can I see your pretty face again?

07:10.388 --> 07:11.889
I'll pick you up later.

07:12.098 --> 07:14.016
I will just stay home today.

07:14.183 --> 07:15.685
I think I should at least do that.

07:22.316 --> 07:25.736
Don't worry.
I know I can get through this.

07:26.946 --> 07:28.114
I have you.

07:30.366 --> 07:31.534
I have

07:32.368 --> 07:35.246
Seo Jun-hui keeping me safe
right by my side,

07:35.329 --> 07:37.290
so nothing scares me.

07:37.790 --> 07:39.292
I'm not scared at all.

07:43.546 --> 07:45.298
- Yoon Jin-a.
- Yes?

07:47.216 --> 07:48.259
I love you.

07:55.725 --> 07:57.351
I really do love you so much.

09:31.946 --> 09:33.990
JUN-HUI: WAITING FOR YOU
ISN'T BORING AT ALL

09:34.073 --> 09:35.908
LOVE U: YOU'RE MAKING ME FEEL WORSE.
I MISS YOU.

09:35.992 --> 09:38.077
JUN-HUI: YOU CAN TAKE YOUR TIME,
BUT I MISS YOU SO MUCH

09:38.160 --> 09:39.954
LOVE U: DAD WENT TO BED!
I'LL BE THERE SHORTLY.

09:40.037 --> 09:41.706
JUN-HUI: HURRY, I'LL GIVE YOU A BIG HUG

09:41.789 --> 09:43.624
JUN-HUI: WE JUST HUNG UP,
AND I ALREADY MISS YOU

09:46.127 --> 09:47.503
Have you eaten yet?

09:49.005 --> 09:50.423
I don't really have any appetite.

09:50.756 --> 09:52.258
So you've been starving all day?

09:54.844 --> 09:56.262
Is there anything you want to eat?

09:56.345 --> 09:57.972
Tell me. I'll treat you.

09:59.307 --> 10:00.391
Nothing.

10:01.309 --> 10:02.935
But you have to eat something.

10:03.019 --> 10:04.520
Anything that comes to mind?

10:05.730 --> 10:06.731
Not really.

10:08.608 --> 10:11.736
Well, I do want something spicy.

10:12.069 --> 10:13.154
Something spicy?

10:14.030 --> 10:15.656
You must want braised kimchi.

10:17.575 --> 10:19.160
I'm starting to crave it now.

10:19.327 --> 10:21.662
Let's go to Jin-a's place.
You love Ms. Kim's braised kimchi.

10:21.746 --> 10:23.664
No, I don't want to bother her.

10:23.914 --> 10:26.751
She always tells us that it's fine

10:26.834 --> 10:29.170
as long as we let her know beforehand.

10:29.587 --> 10:31.547
Give me your phone. Let me call Jin-a.

10:31.631 --> 10:33.716
I'm looking at something right now.

10:35.259 --> 10:38.095
Wait here. I'll bring my purse
after I tell the manager that I'm leaving.

10:46.520 --> 10:47.480
You're here.

10:47.563 --> 10:48.898
- Hi.
- Hello.

10:49.190 --> 10:51.317
Why do you always buy stuff
every time you come over?

10:51.400 --> 10:52.318
That's not necessary.

10:52.401 --> 10:53.861
I just got you some fruits.

10:55.863 --> 10:57.698
- Mr. Yoon, we're here.
- Hey.

10:57.782 --> 10:59.367
- Welcome.
- Hello.

10:59.450 --> 11:00.493
Come on in.

11:00.576 --> 11:02.912
He's been excited about drinking
ever since this morning.

11:02.995 --> 11:04.664
Look at him grilling meat over there.

11:04.747 --> 11:06.999
Mr. Yoon and I really do think alike.

11:07.458 --> 11:09.585
- Where's Jin-a?
- She's still asleep.

11:09.960 --> 11:11.712
How dare she stay in bed when I'm here?

11:24.517 --> 11:25.810
You brat!

11:27.186 --> 11:28.938
What? Who's this?

11:30.022 --> 11:31.148
- Hey.
- What?

11:31.315 --> 11:32.733
What are you doing here?

11:33.067 --> 11:35.319
You didn't tell me you were coming over.

11:36.112 --> 11:37.488
- My gosh.
- My goodness.

11:37.571 --> 11:39.615
Hey. My goodness.

11:40.950 --> 11:42.243
I'm sorry.

11:42.701 --> 11:45.371
- When did you get here?
- Gosh.

11:46.247 --> 11:48.666
I called your mom before coming.

11:48.874 --> 11:52.044
Hey, I know it's your day off,

11:52.128 --> 11:54.171
but why are you still asleep?

11:55.464 --> 11:56.507
What did you do yesterday?

11:58.134 --> 12:00.261
I... I didn't do much.

12:00.678 --> 12:04.348
Why are you stuttering?
You're being weird.

12:04.890 --> 12:06.725
Tell me the truth right now.

12:07.101 --> 12:08.686
What truth?

12:08.769 --> 12:10.980
Hey, come on. Stop.

12:18.112 --> 12:20.281
You made so much braised kimchi.

12:20.364 --> 12:22.450
You said Jun-hui wanted to eat this.

12:22.533 --> 12:24.994
This will surely bring his appetite back.

12:38.924 --> 12:40.551
It must have taken you ages.

12:43.471 --> 12:44.930
- Try some.
- Okay.

12:45.014 --> 12:46.474
It's seasoned perfectly.

12:48.392 --> 12:50.519
Gosh, I'm hungry.

13:00.279 --> 13:03.115
- I need to go make a phone call.
- Okay.

13:09.413 --> 13:10.873
What are you doing here?

13:11.457 --> 13:13.626
Hey, are you crazy?

13:13.709 --> 13:15.586
I couldn't help. I missed you so much.

13:15.669 --> 13:17.087
You must be out of your mind.

13:17.213 --> 13:19.006
- Yes, I know.
- What?

13:19.340 --> 13:20.341
Hey.

13:22.551 --> 13:23.761
Seriously, get out.

13:23.844 --> 13:25.888
- Why?
- What do you mean, "Why"?

13:27.181 --> 13:28.641
Why aren't you saying anything to me?

13:29.058 --> 13:30.059
What do you mean?

13:31.519 --> 13:32.895
I told you I love you.

13:34.271 --> 13:35.314
Oh, that.

13:36.357 --> 13:37.358
"Oh, that"?

13:41.987 --> 13:44.240
- Look at you.
- What did you just say?

13:44.615 --> 13:45.616
Look at you.

13:46.742 --> 13:48.369
Where did they go?

13:50.412 --> 13:52.748
My gosh, what's going on in here?

13:52.831 --> 13:55.668
I told him to get out of my room,
but he wouldn't listen.

13:55.751 --> 13:58.379
- Gosh, please listen to her.
- Seriously.

13:58.462 --> 14:00.297
- When will you grow up?
- Exactly.

14:01.090 --> 14:02.758
I'm hungry. Let's go eat.

14:05.469 --> 14:08.472
Jun-hui, eat up.

14:09.139 --> 14:12.518
And you can come here
anytime you want home-made food.

14:12.601 --> 14:14.812
It doesn't matter if no one's home.

14:14.895 --> 14:16.939
You can just heat something up yourself.

14:17.314 --> 14:18.315
Okay.

14:20.192 --> 14:22.236
He's always picky with what I cook.

14:22.319 --> 14:24.697
But he always enjoys your food.

14:25.197 --> 14:27.491
Once he gets married,
he'll only want his wife's food.

14:27.616 --> 14:30.160
That will depend on
whom he gets married to.

14:30.870 --> 14:32.788
- One of Jin-a's colleagues
- Yes?

14:32.955 --> 14:34.832
has feelings for Jun-hui.

14:35.082 --> 14:36.709
Really? Who is it?

14:36.792 --> 14:39.295
An assistant manager
who oversees my store on behalf of Jin-a.

14:39.378 --> 14:40.921
Her name's Kang Se-yeong.

14:41.005 --> 14:43.549
And she's already trying so hard
to impress me.

14:46.051 --> 14:48.178
- You noticed too, didn't you?
- Of course.

14:50.431 --> 14:51.974
Oh, really?

14:52.057 --> 14:53.183
I noticed right away.

14:54.935 --> 14:56.186
Good for you.

14:58.147 --> 15:00.441
You're really slow-witted, Jin-a.

15:00.566 --> 15:02.276
Even I could tell right away.

15:02.776 --> 15:04.111
Only I didn't know.

15:04.194 --> 15:06.780
Almost every guy
in our building likes her. She's pretty.

15:07.907 --> 15:10.743
Enough about her looks.
What does her family do?

15:11.243 --> 15:12.536
Mom.

15:12.620 --> 15:15.414
What? That's an important factor.

15:15.497 --> 15:17.041
What do her parents do?

15:17.124 --> 15:18.959
How would I know?

15:20.336 --> 15:23.130
Jun-hui, let me tell you something.

15:23.464 --> 15:26.342
You have to take many things into account
when you date someone.

15:26.425 --> 15:29.845
You need to look into her background
as well as her family members.

15:31.096 --> 15:32.723
It's not like our family's that great.

15:32.806 --> 15:34.350
That's why it's more important.

15:34.433 --> 15:37.061
At least your partner should be
from a good background.

15:38.729 --> 15:40.731
Stop talking nonsense.

15:42.066 --> 15:43.233
Let's eat up.

15:43.901 --> 15:46.028
Why is this nonsense?

15:46.111 --> 15:47.988
I'm talking about their future.

15:48.238 --> 15:50.699
They're adults.
They'll take care of it on their own.

15:50.783 --> 15:52.660
Why are you making them feel uneasy?

15:52.743 --> 15:53.744
My goodness.

15:54.578 --> 15:57.414
Did I upset you guys?

15:58.248 --> 15:59.249
Are you going to continue?

15:59.833 --> 16:01.085
If so, I'm going to go in.

16:01.168 --> 16:02.795
Jin-a, relax.

16:03.504 --> 16:05.881
Yes, she was just looking out for us.

16:05.965 --> 16:07.967
That's exactly what I mean.

16:08.717 --> 16:11.637
I may have come off
a little straight-forward,

16:11.720 --> 16:14.890
but I only said what I said
because I care about Jun-hui.

16:15.307 --> 16:17.101
Jun-hui, you understand, right?

16:17.685 --> 16:19.520
Of course. I'm always grateful.

16:19.728 --> 16:23.273
And don't worry. I'll look out for myself.

16:23.941 --> 16:27.695
Okay. Jun-hui, eat this too. Here.

16:37.496 --> 16:39.081
Ms. Geum, I have big news.

16:40.416 --> 16:42.042
The Purchasing Team also had an incident.

16:42.334 --> 16:43.168
What incident?

16:43.293 --> 16:45.295
They were drinking
with the Resources Team.

16:45.379 --> 16:47.464
When Mr. Oh offered Ms. Choi a drink,
she said,

16:48.048 --> 16:49.174
"Don't force me to drink

16:49.258 --> 16:51.301
or I'm going to sue you
for human rights violations."

16:51.719 --> 16:52.970
Isn't that awesome?

16:54.096 --> 16:55.889
Is this the butterfly effect
of Jin-a's action?

16:57.141 --> 16:59.059
It sure was a huge blow.

16:59.435 --> 17:03.355
No one ever imagined
that "Ms. Tambourine," of all people,

17:03.439 --> 17:05.816
- would do something like that.
- True.

17:05.899 --> 17:08.235
But I wonder what's gotten into her.

17:08.318 --> 17:10.779
Whatever the reason,
we should applaud her.

17:11.238 --> 17:14.867
But I hope things don't backfire on us.

17:15.534 --> 17:16.994
I'm worried about that too.

17:17.077 --> 17:19.038
I don't think the higher-ups
will let it slide.

17:19.121 --> 17:20.581
If they don't,

17:21.123 --> 17:23.292
I won't let them get away with it.

17:37.639 --> 17:40.684
NOTICE: FEMALE-EMPLOYEES-ONLY DINNER
HOSTED BY PRESIDENT JO

18:09.463 --> 18:10.506
Go on.

18:15.010 --> 18:16.261
Come in.

18:28.065 --> 18:29.316
Did you read the notice?

18:30.984 --> 18:34.279
Pick a place that's most preferred
by our female employees.

18:34.780 --> 18:35.781
Yes, sir.

18:36.865 --> 18:37.866
One more thing.

18:39.243 --> 18:41.662
I want you to gather information

18:41.787 --> 18:45.415
on every single complaint they might have
regarding discriminations of any kind.

18:45.958 --> 18:48.544
Bring it to me before the dinner.

18:50.587 --> 18:51.755
Yes, sir.

18:53.465 --> 18:56.218
They can remain anonymous,
but I want the assailant's name.

18:56.844 --> 19:01.098
Mr. Jo, I think we should listen
to both sides of the story to avoid bias.

19:01.181 --> 19:03.433
I'll look into the circumstances
afterward.

19:05.894 --> 19:09.148
What's wrong?
Are you also guilty of something?

19:11.608 --> 19:13.360
Only the victim would know.

19:26.623 --> 19:28.584
Hey, where are you going?

19:30.002 --> 19:30.961
Yes.

19:32.171 --> 19:33.297
No.

19:33.881 --> 19:34.965
- "Love U"?
- What the...

19:36.049 --> 19:38.969
- Do you want to die?
- So, you are dating someone.

19:39.052 --> 19:40.012
Mind your own business.

19:40.596 --> 19:41.722
Who is it?

19:42.681 --> 19:44.016
Don't tell me...

19:45.017 --> 19:46.185
What?

19:46.476 --> 19:47.853
Are you dating a married woman?

19:48.729 --> 19:49.563
My gosh.

19:50.147 --> 19:52.316
Judging by that reaction, I must be right.

19:52.858 --> 19:53.901
Who is it?

19:55.527 --> 19:58.864
There's enough time, so don't speed.

20:00.949 --> 20:03.327
Of course, I miss you too.

20:03.869 --> 20:06.079
Okay. See you soon.

20:09.541 --> 20:11.084
I had to call the office,

20:11.168 --> 20:13.128
and I was talking to my co-worker.

20:13.295 --> 20:14.671
Are you dating your coworker?

20:14.963 --> 20:16.632
No, he works at a different company...

20:18.508 --> 20:20.469
Should I make you write
a letter of explanation

20:20.594 --> 20:22.304
or deduct points?

20:22.763 --> 20:25.057
Can I buy you lunch and call it even?

20:25.599 --> 20:28.018
That's more than enough.
But you know what?

20:28.477 --> 20:31.521
Those who date secretly
always make it more obvious.

20:42.491 --> 20:45.202
- Is it good?
- Yes, try it.

20:49.373 --> 20:50.457
It's so good.

20:51.708 --> 20:54.002
What?
We've done even more intimate things.

20:55.045 --> 20:57.214
You are not shy about anything now.

20:57.297 --> 20:58.507
Why? Should I go on?

21:04.972 --> 21:06.723
When we came here before,

21:08.892 --> 21:11.645
I tried to ask you to go out with me

21:13.522 --> 21:15.274
about a thousand times, but couldn't.

21:16.525 --> 21:18.235
Did you know that?

21:19.486 --> 21:22.698
I was so frustrated
that it nearly killed me.

21:25.742 --> 21:29.413
But that time when we first met...

21:29.788 --> 21:33.709
I mean the time we saw each other
after a long time.

21:34.084 --> 21:35.919
Why did you pretend
like you didn't see me?

21:42.718 --> 21:44.428
I was taking my bicycle
outside the office,

21:45.345 --> 21:47.347
and there was a woman
walking toward me from afar.

21:47.764 --> 21:49.182
Strangely, I was intrigued by her.

21:50.684 --> 21:52.436
Men are all the same.

21:53.437 --> 21:55.022
It wasn't like that.

21:55.772 --> 21:59.401
I just wanted to catch a glimpse of her,
but she was so pretty.

21:59.860 --> 22:02.112
The moment I thought, "Wow, she's pretty,"

22:03.155 --> 22:05.032
I realized that it was you.

22:05.615 --> 22:07.909
- Were you disappointed?
- I was surprised.

22:09.036 --> 22:10.871
I thought,
"Is that really the Jin-a I know?

22:11.455 --> 22:13.123
Has she always been this pretty?"

22:13.206 --> 22:14.499
It is you.

22:14.583 --> 22:17.461
- I highly doubt that.
- I thought I was mistaken.

22:17.544 --> 22:19.963
- When did you come back?
- Seriously, I'm telling you the truth.

23:18.897 --> 23:20.357
Cheers, everyone.

23:20.440 --> 23:22.776
- Cheers. Nice to meet you.
- Cheers.

25:05.879 --> 25:08.381
That's cheating. I was asleep.

25:08.632 --> 25:10.300
You shouldn't have fallen asleep then.

25:11.301 --> 25:14.054
- You fell asleep first.
- You should've woken me up.

25:16.848 --> 25:18.016
I should have.

25:23.521 --> 25:24.981
What are you laughing at?

25:26.191 --> 25:29.778
I don't know what it is. It's just funny.

25:34.199 --> 25:36.201
Gosh, I'm in big trouble.

25:36.743 --> 25:37.827
Why?

25:39.079 --> 25:42.415
I want to let the world know
that you're mine

25:42.499 --> 25:44.042
because you're so pretty.

25:46.795 --> 25:50.423
Honestly, this is serious.
I might get ill.

25:51.258 --> 25:52.425
Whatever.

25:54.803 --> 25:56.179
So I was wondering

25:58.265 --> 25:59.933
if you would like to meet my friends.

26:01.101 --> 26:02.269
Your friends?

26:05.313 --> 26:07.899
They're going camping
with their girlfriends,

26:08.400 --> 26:10.110
and they'll let me join
if I bring a partner.

26:14.281 --> 26:16.116
I told them I'll think about it.

26:16.199 --> 26:17.659
It's okay if you don't want to.

26:18.034 --> 26:19.411
It's not that.

26:19.911 --> 26:20.954
If they're all couples,

26:21.830 --> 26:23.456
I might feel a bit intimidated.

26:26.584 --> 26:29.129
Looking at me like that doesn't help.

26:29.462 --> 26:31.298
I'll probably be the oldest.

26:34.134 --> 26:35.343
My goodness.

26:38.138 --> 26:39.264
Stop.

27:18.678 --> 27:20.388
It is indeed shocking.

27:21.848 --> 27:24.267
Being in a bind

27:24.351 --> 27:27.062
is the exact expression
to describe this situation.

27:28.021 --> 27:30.106
How can I take advantage of this?

27:30.940 --> 27:34.194
I'll be at your service forever, Ms. Geum.

27:34.652 --> 27:36.988
Hey, I'm not that petty.

27:37.614 --> 27:39.908
I'm talking about how I should use this
against Se-yeong.

27:41.368 --> 27:43.578
She's so full of hope.

27:44.120 --> 27:48.249
The girl who always gets what she wants
is trying to score once again,

27:48.750 --> 27:51.961
but takes a blow from an unexpected rival.

27:53.088 --> 27:54.756
Isn't it so entertaining already?

27:55.215 --> 27:57.384
Please cut me some slack.

28:00.095 --> 28:02.180
I did think there would be a reason

28:02.389 --> 28:04.349
why you became a different person.

28:05.141 --> 28:06.309
You're admirable.

28:06.559 --> 28:08.812
I said, cut me some slack.

28:08.895 --> 28:11.147
I'm not teasing you. I mean it.

28:11.523 --> 28:13.608
I want to applaud you for your courage.

28:16.319 --> 28:17.779
I really mean it.

28:19.447 --> 28:21.491
Thank you from the bottom of my heart.

28:21.950 --> 28:23.993
It isn't like I'm giving
my consent to adultery.

28:24.077 --> 28:27.122
Anyway, you should buy me dinner later.

28:28.498 --> 28:29.707
Come alone.

28:29.999 --> 28:32.293
Don't show up with him
and start making out in front of me.

28:36.714 --> 28:38.675
Would you like some tea, Ms. Geum?

28:43.471 --> 28:44.514
Hi.

28:45.348 --> 28:46.975
Good morning.

28:48.643 --> 28:50.145
Did something good happen or what?

28:51.229 --> 28:52.272
Do I look happy?

28:52.772 --> 28:55.692
Yes, you look a little different today.

28:56.067 --> 28:58.153
You look as if you started seeing someone.

29:00.488 --> 29:01.740
Did you really?

29:03.158 --> 29:03.992
Hello.

29:04.743 --> 29:06.745
- Hello.
- Hello, Jun-hui.

29:29.058 --> 29:30.602
What's your schedule like today?

29:32.228 --> 29:33.605
I always have a full schedule.

29:33.688 --> 29:35.940
I have to head out
right after our meeting.

29:38.151 --> 29:40.487
I'd love to go somewhere nice for a day

29:40.570 --> 29:42.572
so that I can clear my head.

29:43.323 --> 29:46.409
I want to take you out
to a nice restaurant for a meal,

29:46.743 --> 29:48.119
but if you're busy, that's too bad.

29:50.330 --> 29:51.998
My afternoon will be a busy one.

29:53.166 --> 29:55.919
Do you have plans for lunch today?

29:59.464 --> 30:00.381
Fortunately, no.

30:02.550 --> 30:05.303
Then shall we have lunch together?

30:06.137 --> 30:08.890
That'd be great.
Think about where you'd like to go.

30:08.973 --> 30:10.475
Wherever it is, I'll treat you.

30:11.476 --> 30:12.602
Okay.

30:19.442 --> 30:20.777
I was just kidding.

30:30.328 --> 30:31.371
What was that about?

30:32.997 --> 30:35.458
I'm talking about Seo Jun-hui.

30:36.709 --> 30:37.961
You said you're busy today.

30:38.878 --> 30:40.964
I was just looking for someone
to have lunch with.

30:42.131 --> 30:44.759
But why are you being so anxious?

30:45.134 --> 30:47.053
I must say, it's so unlike you.

30:49.222 --> 30:51.182
- Good morning.
- Hello.

31:21.671 --> 31:24.424
Ms. Kang, if you're heading out now,

31:24.549 --> 31:25.967
can you drop me off at the station?

31:26.050 --> 31:28.052
What are those legs for?

31:28.261 --> 31:29.304
Just walk.

31:37.562 --> 31:40.440
It's not like the meeting went bad.
What's with her today?

31:42.358 --> 31:43.943
What's wrong, Ms. Geum?

31:44.527 --> 31:45.445
Don't mind me.

31:45.945 --> 31:47.447
Rewrite the sales report.

31:48.323 --> 31:49.574
Right on it, sir.

31:53.161 --> 31:54.203
My gosh.

31:59.542 --> 32:02.795
Why does Mr. Jo want to organize
the company dinner?

32:03.671 --> 32:06.633
I think he just wants
to encourage our female employees.

32:08.134 --> 32:11.471
Well, I know that he's organizing it,

32:12.096 --> 32:15.808
but if he'd like the executives
to attend as well, I will--

32:15.892 --> 32:18.353
He hasn't mentioned
anything about that, sir.

32:20.313 --> 32:22.774
All right, then. Anything else?

32:22.857 --> 32:23.900
No, sir.

32:25.777 --> 32:26.819
You can leave.

32:42.835 --> 32:43.920
Well...

32:47.256 --> 32:49.926
Something is definitely up
with the female employees.

32:50.385 --> 32:52.136
Geum Bo-ra is acting like Yoon Jin-a.

32:52.428 --> 32:54.681
She's suddenly become obedient.

32:56.391 --> 32:58.101
What the heck is going on?

32:58.768 --> 33:01.145
Do you have any idea
what it could be about?

33:02.105 --> 33:03.523
No, I have no idea.

33:03.856 --> 33:07.443
But I think that we should be careful
whenever we have

33:07.777 --> 33:09.404
any interactions
with the female employees.

33:09.487 --> 33:12.073
We should be careful?
We didn't even do anything.

33:14.242 --> 33:16.828
I mean, when we go out together
and have a drink or two--

33:16.911 --> 33:18.413
That's what you shouldn't do.

33:20.999 --> 33:24.794
He's right. For the next little while,

33:25.253 --> 33:27.755
we shouldn't have any team dinners.
No team dinners whatsoever.

33:35.805 --> 33:36.806
When did you get here?

33:39.058 --> 33:41.310
Geum Bo-ra totally beat me.

33:42.645 --> 33:43.688
I'm speechless.

33:43.855 --> 33:45.690
What? What did Bo-ra do?

33:45.857 --> 33:47.400
Did something happen?

33:47.483 --> 33:50.737
It's about Seo Jun-hui.
She snatched him away from me.

33:52.155 --> 33:54.073
- What?
- You find it hard to believe too, right?

33:54.157 --> 33:55.575
I'm so speechless.

33:56.200 --> 33:58.494
Seriously...
Does it even make sense to you?

34:00.371 --> 34:01.873
- Hello.
- Hello.

34:01.956 --> 34:05.543
She asked him out for lunch
right in front of me.

34:05.626 --> 34:06.919
And what's crazier is...

34:07.587 --> 34:10.256
he gladly said yes.

34:13.551 --> 34:16.888
I know. You can't help but laugh
because it's so crazy.

34:16.971 --> 34:18.056
I'm sorry.

34:18.806 --> 34:20.349
What should I do now?

34:21.100 --> 34:23.311
I have to stop her
before she makes more progress.

34:26.064 --> 34:27.148
Se-yeong.

34:27.690 --> 34:30.193
It doesn't have to be him.
There are so many guys who like you.

34:30.401 --> 34:31.736
It's Geum Bo-ra of all people.

34:31.819 --> 34:34.197
Should I just watch her
take him away from me?

34:34.572 --> 34:36.407
Do you think my pride will allow that?

34:36.991 --> 34:38.451
No, I cannot let that happen.

34:45.500 --> 34:47.168
I should try to charm his sister first.

34:48.377 --> 34:51.547
You're quite close to her, right?
You said she's your best friend.

34:51.631 --> 34:52.965
Se-yeong.

34:53.591 --> 34:56.135
Help me out here, please?

34:56.219 --> 34:59.013
Well, I understand how you feel,

35:00.389 --> 35:03.810
but I don't think
there's anything I can do to help you.

35:04.560 --> 35:05.812
You're a bad friend.

35:05.895 --> 35:07.522
I'll bring you a new one.

35:08.648 --> 35:09.649
Hey.

35:10.233 --> 35:12.652
That's enough.
Just come and eat this with us.

35:13.820 --> 35:14.904
I don't want to gain weight.

35:14.987 --> 35:16.405
You won't gain weight from this.

35:17.115 --> 35:19.158
This is very good for women.

35:19.242 --> 35:21.744
Collagen is excellent for anti-aging.

35:22.078 --> 35:25.248
Right, collagen. I do need some collagen.

36:09.625 --> 36:11.335
- Goodness.
- Gosh! You startled me.

36:11.419 --> 36:14.672
What the heck are you doing now?

36:15.339 --> 36:17.425
Dear me.

36:18.676 --> 36:19.552
Gosh.

36:19.635 --> 36:22.138
IN ORDER TO MAKE YOU LOOK YOUNGER
WITH MAKEUP, MAKE YOUR SKIN LOOK

36:22.221 --> 36:25.016
AS HYDRATED AND RADIANT AS POSSIBLE
WITH HYDRATING BB CREAM OR FOUNDATION

37:29.247 --> 37:31.207
You look pretty enough.
You don't need that.

37:31.290 --> 37:33.834
My skin looks rough
because I couldn't sleep last night.

37:34.669 --> 37:35.503
What should I do?

37:37.213 --> 37:38.631
No, don't look.

37:38.714 --> 37:40.508
- Why not? Let me see.
- I don't have time.

37:40.591 --> 37:41.634
Come on.

37:46.973 --> 37:48.307
By the way, how old are they?

37:49.475 --> 37:52.395
Like I said, there's no need
for you to feel insecure.

37:53.145 --> 37:54.355
They're young.

37:55.398 --> 37:56.983
I want to know how young they are.

38:11.789 --> 38:13.582
Why are you so nervous?

38:14.083 --> 38:15.960
I'll be the oldest one there.

38:16.502 --> 38:18.462
They're not in the same league as you are.

38:19.672 --> 38:20.840
Trust me.

38:21.465 --> 38:22.675
I can't.

38:23.718 --> 38:25.970
- It will work out anyway.
- I don't think so.

38:26.053 --> 38:27.722
- Seriously.
- This is delicious.

38:27.805 --> 38:29.765
Hey, you're the youngest one here.

38:30.266 --> 38:31.559
I told you, didn't I?

38:31.642 --> 38:33.561
That's heavy. I'll do it.

38:33.686 --> 38:34.770
- Really?
- What did you eat?

38:35.354 --> 38:37.231
- You don't eat sea pineapples.
- Have you heard?

38:37.315 --> 38:39.817
- Ji-hye, that's heavy. I'll do it.
- Oh, really?

38:39.900 --> 38:41.319
- I was so startled.
- Me too.

38:41.402 --> 38:42.403
Did you hear, Hyeong-gyu?

38:42.486 --> 38:45.489
- Where should I move this?
- Over there.

38:46.407 --> 38:47.575
I didn't know.

38:48.659 --> 38:50.745
- I know what you're up to.
- I'll put it here.

38:51.370 --> 38:53.372
You're helping out a lot today.

38:53.456 --> 38:54.665
I always help out.

38:55.583 --> 38:56.709
Hyeong-gyu.

38:58.294 --> 39:00.421
We can do that later, can't we?

39:00.504 --> 39:02.965
- Do you need help with anything?
- No.

39:03.049 --> 39:05.676
- We should talk about that in detail.
- Is it awkward?

39:05.760 --> 39:08.554
- That is so out of the blue. I'm fine.
- Aren't I right?

39:08.637 --> 39:09.680
The reason for that is...

39:10.181 --> 39:12.558
- Jun-hui, come take a look at this.
- I mean, he's my friend.

39:12.892 --> 39:14.769
- It won't stay still.
- Okay.

39:15.895 --> 39:17.355
- I'll be right back.
- Okay.

39:17.646 --> 39:19.690
I knew he'd be like that.

39:19.774 --> 39:21.025
How did you know?

39:21.942 --> 39:24.153
- Isn't this weird?
- How did you make this?

39:26.864 --> 39:28.157
I was right, wasn't I?

39:28.657 --> 39:31.285
- You're the prettiest one.
- Forget it.

39:33.829 --> 39:35.790
This is my first time
seeing Jun-hui's girlfriend.

39:36.165 --> 39:37.208
Me too.

39:39.960 --> 39:41.170
She's pretty, right?

39:41.504 --> 39:43.672
- My gosh.
- Seriously.

39:44.256 --> 39:47.009
- What? What's wrong? She's pretty.
- She is.

39:47.593 --> 39:49.929
She's older than us, isn't she?
How old are you?

39:50.012 --> 39:52.890
Hey, why would you ask her that?
It's rude.

39:53.557 --> 39:54.725
Is it?

40:08.531 --> 40:11.534
I'll be turning 40 soon.

40:17.206 --> 40:18.874
You look so young.

40:19.667 --> 40:22.044
- Really?
- I wouldn't have been able to guess.

40:26.215 --> 40:28.217
We can do it. You can rest.

40:28.509 --> 40:29.677
No, I'll help.

40:29.760 --> 40:32.054
No, it's okay. You can rest.

40:32.138 --> 40:33.931
- He's right. We're almost done.
- Go on.

40:34.306 --> 40:35.433
Just take a break.

40:42.982 --> 40:45.568
- We'll do it.
- It's okay. I'm almost done.

40:46.068 --> 40:47.486
- We'll do it.
- You can rest.

40:47.570 --> 40:48.529
- But...
- It's okay.

40:48.612 --> 40:49.697
- Oh, be careful.
- Oh, no.

40:49.864 --> 40:51.949
- Go take a break.
- We'll do it.

40:56.162 --> 40:58.080
We should've brought more pots.

40:58.831 --> 41:00.040
Hurry up.

41:00.416 --> 41:02.376
- Good work.
- Do I get anything?

41:03.627 --> 41:04.712
Do I get a prize?

41:04.795 --> 41:07.715
We can't drink because we have to drive,
so let's play foot volleyball.

41:08.215 --> 41:10.092
- No thanks.
- Why would we play foot volleyball?

41:10.176 --> 41:11.093
- Don't you dare.
- What?

41:11.177 --> 41:12.428
- Let me do that.
- It's okay.

41:12.511 --> 41:14.972
- We can't play with just four players.
- I'll take this.

41:15.055 --> 41:16.223
That little punk.

41:17.766 --> 41:19.226
Are we not going to play?

41:20.311 --> 41:22.146
It sounds fun. Why aren't we playing?

41:23.147 --> 41:24.273
Are you going to play?

41:24.857 --> 41:26.192
Okay, let's go.

41:26.734 --> 41:28.319
- Nice shot.
- Don't touch it.

41:28.402 --> 41:29.320
It's out.

41:31.655 --> 41:33.532
- Oh, no.
- What am I supposed to do?

41:34.950 --> 41:36.035
Nice.

41:38.829 --> 41:39.663
Kick it.

41:49.089 --> 41:50.299
She did it.

41:52.718 --> 41:53.719
I got it!

41:57.765 --> 41:59.099
- Jun-hui, get it.
- The wind...

41:59.892 --> 42:01.477
Head it. Nice.

42:02.728 --> 42:04.313
Great. That was nice.

42:08.067 --> 42:09.193
Nice.

42:10.903 --> 42:12.947
- My gosh.
- He got it.

42:13.948 --> 42:15.658
Nice. Head it.

42:17.993 --> 42:19.119
What was that?

42:20.579 --> 42:21.747
She did it.

42:22.456 --> 42:23.749
- Keep going.
- Mine.

42:28.295 --> 42:29.255
Come on.

42:29.797 --> 42:31.006
You should've gotten that.

42:31.882 --> 42:33.008
That was good.

42:36.345 --> 42:37.972
Let's play another round.

42:38.639 --> 42:41.183
Over 40cm of snow has piled up...

42:41.267 --> 42:42.977
Why did she have to go on a trip?

42:43.060 --> 42:45.187
UP TO 40CM OF HEAVY SNOWFALL IN GANGWON-DO

42:45.271 --> 42:46.272
Was that Jin-a?

42:46.355 --> 42:49.483
Yes. She said she'll be here tomorrow
because of the snow.

42:50.317 --> 42:54.822
But do you think she really went
with her co-workers?

42:56.448 --> 42:58.492
It will stop raining and snowing

42:58.576 --> 43:00.995
by late afternoon tomorrow.

43:09.211 --> 43:12.089
- Did she scold you?
- She was just worried.

43:13.424 --> 43:14.675
Maybe we shouldn't have come.

43:15.342 --> 43:17.094
I know you don't mean that.

43:17.219 --> 43:18.304
You got me.

43:24.184 --> 43:25.477
Thanks for today.

43:25.978 --> 43:27.563
I know you tried your best for me.

43:27.646 --> 43:29.773
What do mean? I had so much fun.

43:29.857 --> 43:31.233
Let's do this again next time.

43:33.902 --> 43:36.572
Gosh, you're so adorable.

43:40.034 --> 43:41.577
You must still feel awkward with them.

43:42.036 --> 43:43.495
Do you think you can sleep with them?

43:44.121 --> 43:45.456
The awkwardness doesn't matter.

43:45.706 --> 43:48.292
I'm just sad they're not guys.

43:49.710 --> 43:51.170
You have a guy right here.

43:53.464 --> 43:54.632
I know.

43:56.050 --> 43:57.134
Gosh.

43:59.928 --> 44:02.181
- Should we go inside?
- It's snowing too much. Let's go.

44:09.688 --> 44:12.441
Just enter any restaurant you see.

44:12.524 --> 44:14.276
- Right.
- They're all delicious.

44:14.360 --> 44:15.653
- I'm serious.
- What did you eat?

44:15.736 --> 44:17.154
There's sushi and ramen.

44:17.237 --> 44:18.572
- I love sushi.
- Udon's good too.

44:18.656 --> 44:20.658
- Gosh, udon.
- There's also nabe.

44:20.741 --> 44:23.077
- Nabe's also really delicious.
- What's nabe?

44:23.160 --> 44:26.413
It's that dish
where you boil everything in a pot.

44:26.497 --> 44:28.165
Jin-a, you can use anything you need.

44:28.248 --> 44:29.708
But I'm not sure if they'll suit you.

44:31.210 --> 44:32.544
I can use anything.

44:32.628 --> 44:34.672
I also carry my makeup bag with me,

44:34.755 --> 44:37.257
but you guys are on
a totally different level.

44:38.717 --> 44:40.678
I keep my makeup in my boyfriend's car

44:40.761 --> 44:42.304
just in case anything like this happens.

44:42.388 --> 44:44.390
I know you make it happen on purpose.

44:44.723 --> 44:46.684
Yes, she probably made it snow tonight.

44:46.767 --> 44:48.769
She is almighty.

44:48.852 --> 44:49.937
How did you guys know?

44:50.938 --> 44:53.315
Jin-a, you're an office worker,
aren't you?

44:53.399 --> 44:54.983
I envy you so much.

44:55.067 --> 44:57.403
I went to grad school
because I couldn't get a job.

44:59.238 --> 45:02.199
I heard that's often the case these days.

45:02.908 --> 45:05.244
At least you went to grad school.

45:05.702 --> 45:07.496
I work part-time and spend all the money

45:07.579 --> 45:10.249
on getting my resume edited.

45:10.958 --> 45:13.127
Getting a job isn't the end of it.

45:13.210 --> 45:16.422
Look at me. It's my fourth job,
and I want to quit again.

45:16.588 --> 45:17.756
Why?

45:18.882 --> 45:20.843
At all the companies I've worked for,

45:20.926 --> 45:23.220
making coffee was everything
female workers did.

45:24.179 --> 45:26.056
I studied hard to get a job.

45:26.432 --> 45:28.559
But they treat me
as if I'm their secretary

45:28.934 --> 45:31.061
and leave me out
of all the important tasks.

45:32.813 --> 45:34.773
I've been through all that myself.

45:35.482 --> 45:37.443
- You too?
- Of course.

45:45.617 --> 45:48.245
Are we at a Buddhist temple?
Why aren't we talking?

45:49.455 --> 45:50.622
Then you start talking.

45:53.167 --> 45:56.378
It's no fun when it's just the guys.

45:57.087 --> 45:59.465
Why are the girls so quiet?

46:01.425 --> 46:02.426
Seriously?

46:03.135 --> 46:04.470
That's crazy.

46:04.803 --> 46:07.389
When they say something like that,
you have to teach them a lesson.

46:07.473 --> 46:09.183
- So true.
- Yes.

46:09.266 --> 46:11.894
- You're hilarious.
- I think I have a crush on her.

46:12.352 --> 46:13.562
- What are you doing?
- Cheers.

46:13.645 --> 46:14.980
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

46:16.648 --> 46:17.566
Just a second.

46:17.649 --> 46:19.026
- Oh, my gosh.
- Hey.

46:19.651 --> 46:22.029
- Get out of here.
- Go away.

46:22.237 --> 46:23.989
- Hey, go back down.
- Go downstairs.

46:24.072 --> 46:25.908
- Get out.
- Go.

46:26.492 --> 46:27.451
My gosh.

46:36.084 --> 46:37.878
- Bye.
- Bye.

46:38.045 --> 46:40.714
- See you again.
- Yes, definitely.

46:40.797 --> 46:42.758
- I'll contact you.
- Okay.

46:42.841 --> 46:44.426
- I'll miss you so much.
- Bye.

46:44.968 --> 46:47.137
I'll go now. Call me.

46:49.306 --> 46:51.225
- Bye.
- Bye.

46:55.521 --> 46:56.522
Bye.

46:56.605 --> 46:58.690
- I've never been jealous of women before.
- Call me.

46:58.774 --> 47:00.734
- Be careful. They might steal me from you.
- Bye.

47:01.401 --> 47:02.236
Get in.

50:10.465 --> 50:12.551
Here's your coffee.

50:12.634 --> 50:14.386
Thanks.

50:16.388 --> 50:18.807
Why did you bring so many things? My gosh.

50:19.516 --> 50:22.728
I had to be in the area, so I thought
I should bring you a few side dishes.

50:23.562 --> 50:26.022
You brought pickles too.
It looks delicious.

50:26.189 --> 50:27.315
Thanks for this.

50:28.650 --> 50:30.068
Do you have a get-together?

50:30.694 --> 50:32.112
It's just something casual.

50:32.738 --> 50:35.615
A friend of mine's oldest daughter
got married last year,

50:35.782 --> 50:37.951
and her son is getting married soon.

50:38.034 --> 50:39.911
She wants to treat me
because she feels bad.

50:40.162 --> 50:43.874
Gosh, how could I possibly
enjoy the meal there?

50:45.000 --> 50:47.002
Jin-a is always the problem, isn't she?

50:47.335 --> 50:48.670
Don't even get me started.

50:48.962 --> 50:52.257
Hey, do you know any nice guy
you can set her up with?

50:52.340 --> 50:56.303
Don't even. I brought it up when we were
having drinks with Jun-hui the other day,

50:56.386 --> 50:58.138
and they got so mad at me.

50:58.388 --> 51:00.182
They both glared at me like crazy.

51:00.265 --> 51:02.809
I guess Jin-a can react like that,
but why did Jun-hui get mad?

51:03.268 --> 51:05.020
He just doesn't think it's a good idea

51:05.103 --> 51:06.813
to set her up
with someone I don't know well.

51:08.565 --> 51:10.192
Let's just leave her be.

51:10.275 --> 51:12.444
They say the right one comes along
unexpectedly.

51:12.986 --> 51:14.613
- Well...
- Yes?

51:15.155 --> 51:16.740
I think she's seeing someone.

51:16.823 --> 51:17.657
Really?

51:17.991 --> 51:20.160
- She was away for work recently, you know.
- Right.

51:20.243 --> 51:22.454
She told me that she went with her boss,

51:22.537 --> 51:25.457
but one of our neighbors saw a guy
picking her up.

51:25.540 --> 51:28.627
Apparently, it was a young, handsome guy.

51:30.754 --> 51:33.298
Ms. Kim, that was Jun-hui.

51:33.381 --> 51:34.299
Jun-hui?

51:34.382 --> 51:36.551
He drove her when he was
going for a drive to brainstorm.

51:36.635 --> 51:37.803
I only found out recently too.

51:38.386 --> 51:39.387
My goodness.

51:39.846 --> 51:41.681
Of course, what was I expecting?

51:42.015 --> 51:44.226
I'm an idiot for thinking
that she might have someone.

51:44.726 --> 51:46.728
The thing is, she went on a trip

51:46.812 --> 51:49.272
to Gangwon-do with her coworkers,

51:49.356 --> 51:52.108
so I was thinking that she might actually
be seeing someone.

51:52.651 --> 51:54.528
She went on a trip? With whom?

51:55.153 --> 51:58.448
Ms. Geum and someone else.
But how would I know?

51:58.532 --> 52:00.325
All I can do is just believe
what she tells me.

52:01.117 --> 52:02.619
Good for her.

52:02.702 --> 52:05.622
She needs to have some fun
with her coworkers to relieve stress.

52:05.705 --> 52:09.835
Anyhow, I was being serious earlier.

52:09.918 --> 52:12.921
Please try to find a nice guy for Jin-a.

52:13.380 --> 52:17.300
She always listens to your advice,
you know.

52:17.759 --> 52:19.010
That is true.

52:19.219 --> 52:21.847
Okay, I'll keep my eyes peeled
and do my best to find a guy for her.

52:40.949 --> 52:42.200
I should...

52:43.326 --> 52:44.870
really go in now.

52:46.204 --> 52:47.330
Just one more minute.

52:48.540 --> 52:51.042
Okay, 59, 58, 57,

52:51.126 --> 52:52.836
- 56, 55--
- You're counting down too fast.

52:53.461 --> 52:54.462
My gosh!

52:57.966 --> 52:59.050
That's my mom, right?

52:59.593 --> 53:00.677
I think so.

53:05.056 --> 53:06.600
- What should we do?
- Did she see us?

53:06.683 --> 53:07.893
No, she didn't.

53:08.977 --> 53:09.978
Hold on.

53:17.444 --> 53:18.653
Is she gone?

53:21.698 --> 53:22.741
Yes.

53:38.214 --> 53:39.758
Why do we have to be like this?

53:42.427 --> 53:45.263
It's not like we're absolutely
not allowed to date each other.

53:45.972 --> 53:48.058
Why do we have to feel like
we're committing a crime?

53:49.434 --> 53:51.019
It's nothing new.

53:51.227 --> 53:52.812
I know that,

53:53.313 --> 53:55.732
but maybe we are hiding it
from everyone when we don't have to.

53:56.900 --> 53:57.984
Who knows?

53:58.318 --> 54:00.487
They might be happy for us
when we tell them.

54:02.948 --> 54:05.492
My parents will faint,

54:06.785 --> 54:10.455
and Gyeong-seon will probably go berserk.

54:11.289 --> 54:12.499
She definitely will.

54:12.582 --> 54:14.250
Then why are you bringing it up?

54:16.127 --> 54:18.088
Until when do we have to keep it
from everyone?

54:18.505 --> 54:21.049
I mean, everyone will find out eventually.

54:21.591 --> 54:22.926
It's just a matter of time.

54:23.134 --> 54:24.219
We should just--

54:24.427 --> 54:25.553
For just a little longer.

54:26.513 --> 54:27.889
Let's wait just a bit longer.

54:32.936 --> 54:34.604
Is it because I'm not good enough for you?

54:44.906 --> 54:46.700
Then what could the problem be?

54:47.826 --> 54:51.830
Well, there's someone
who can be a bit of a headache.

54:52.455 --> 54:55.375
Goodness, are you trying
to put the blame on me?

54:55.458 --> 54:58.128
No, of course not. I'm all prepared.

54:59.004 --> 55:00.922
I can go up and tell them right now.

55:02.090 --> 55:05.343
I'll say, "Ms. Kim and Mr. Yoon,
I love Jin-a.

55:05.927 --> 55:07.303
Please allow me to date her."

55:09.931 --> 55:14.185
"Not a chance. Over my dead body."

55:15.854 --> 55:17.230
Then I'll just give up.

55:18.523 --> 55:21.860
You're the one who seduced me.
How can a man give up so quickly?

55:24.738 --> 55:25.864
Come here.

55:27.073 --> 55:28.658
How can I give up on you?

55:29.492 --> 55:30.994
I've finally found the one.

55:33.663 --> 55:36.332
List ten reasons why you like me.

55:39.586 --> 55:40.962
Is that too many?

55:41.671 --> 55:44.424
Yes, it is. There's only one reason.

55:44.799 --> 55:46.051
Just one?

55:48.470 --> 55:49.679
I like you because it's you.

55:50.889 --> 55:52.140
There are no other reasons.

55:59.147 --> 56:02.609
But if you try to find more reasons,
I'm sure you'll be able to...

56:03.276 --> 56:04.819
Right, you're pretty.

56:05.570 --> 56:06.571
You're so pretty.

56:06.988 --> 56:10.784
I know you're saying that
because you can't find ten reasons.

56:12.077 --> 56:15.288
Well, you're pretty.
You look innocent and...

56:17.248 --> 56:18.500
You're beautiful.

56:20.251 --> 56:21.586
Don't be so difficult.

56:22.462 --> 56:24.756
Your boyfriend has to work all night.

56:24.923 --> 56:27.300
Is it so hard to give me a kiss
to cheer me up?

56:28.510 --> 56:30.178
How could you say no?

56:31.513 --> 56:34.140
You'll lose your job for goofing around.

56:34.933 --> 56:37.811
Just like someone I know, this company
can't survive without me.

56:38.770 --> 56:40.396
There's someone like that?

56:40.480 --> 56:41.940
Who can't live without you?

56:42.023 --> 56:44.442
I might leave all my work behind
and go to you.

56:44.526 --> 56:45.693
Do as you please.

56:47.862 --> 56:49.072
Do you think I can't?

56:49.823 --> 56:51.825
All right, fine.

56:58.540 --> 56:59.457
You wish!

57:01.126 --> 57:02.210
Gosh.

57:43.418 --> 57:44.252
LOVE U: CHEER UP!

58:19.287 --> 58:20.663
What's with the color on your lips?

58:21.206 --> 58:23.458
It's a new one, so I tried it on. Why?

58:25.168 --> 58:26.586
Did you not hear from Gyu-min?

58:27.754 --> 58:30.215
Why are you bringing him up
all of a sudden?

58:35.678 --> 58:36.846
What is this?

58:38.681 --> 58:40.225
I didn't want to tell you.

58:40.475 --> 58:42.310
But I can't just let it slide.

58:42.852 --> 58:44.646
Was he always this much of a scumbag?

58:52.403 --> 58:54.239
Where did you get this?

58:54.822 --> 58:56.741
Inside the flower basket.
Jun-hui brought it.

59:02.372 --> 59:04.707
Jun-hui saw this?

59:05.041 --> 59:07.669
He even went to Gyu-min's house
and almost killed that asshole.

59:08.086 --> 59:10.296
Jun-hui smashed his laptop and everything.

59:38.366 --> 59:39.200
Jin-a.

59:39.909 --> 59:42.745
Hey, why are you doing this?

59:42.829 --> 59:44.247
Why are you doing this?

59:44.330 --> 59:47.417
Jin-a, are you crazy?
What the hell are you doing?

59:47.667 --> 59:49.794
Pull yourself together. Come on.

59:49.877 --> 59:51.838
What... What's the problem?

59:51.921 --> 59:53.506
What is it?

59:53.590 --> 59:55.049
Get it together!

59:55.133 --> 59:58.344
Seriously, why are you being like this?

59:58.636 --> 59:59.637
Hey!

01:00:00.138 --> 01:00:02.890
Hey, what the hell is wrong with you?

01:00:03.057 --> 01:00:05.226
What's wrong with you?

01:00:05.560 --> 01:00:08.229
Seriously, what's going on?

01:00:08.396 --> 01:00:09.480
Let go!

01:00:29.792 --> 01:00:30.835
Hello?

01:00:32.545 --> 01:00:33.379
What?

01:00:44.182 --> 01:00:46.351
- Where are you going?
- I'm meeting Jun-hui.

01:00:47.018 --> 01:00:49.520
Why are you meeting him at this late hour?

01:00:50.563 --> 01:00:51.564
Gosh.

01:00:51.648 --> 01:00:54.651
He should be meeting people
who can benefit him in the future.

01:00:55.902 --> 01:00:57.987
Like sister, like brother.

01:00:58.071 --> 01:01:01.366
Why can't they get enough of
Jun-hui and Gyeong-seon?

01:01:02.200 --> 01:01:05.370
Didn't Jin-a go out to meet Gyeong-seon?

01:01:06.120 --> 01:01:07.664
That's exactly why I'm saying this.

01:01:24.180 --> 01:01:26.307
- Are you home?
- This is bad.

01:01:27.725 --> 01:01:30.436
What's with the drama?
Is the game not running on your computer?

01:01:30.895 --> 01:01:33.231
I'm serious.
Jin-a's at the police station.

01:02:37.545 --> 01:02:39.297
What is it? What happened?

01:02:39.589 --> 01:02:40.798
I don't know the details.

01:02:41.007 --> 01:02:43.676
She told me not to tell our parents
and asked me to come here.

01:02:45.011 --> 01:02:46.888
I shouldn't have told her about Gyu-min.

01:02:52.268 --> 01:02:53.478
How can I help you?

01:02:55.563 --> 01:02:57.774
- You son of a bitch.
- Hey, calm down.

01:02:57.857 --> 01:02:59.984
- Let go. Let go of me!
- Hey!

01:03:00.276 --> 01:03:01.652
- Calm down, sir.
- Hey!

01:03:02.528 --> 01:03:05.072
- Come on, let go of me.
- What's wrong with you?

01:03:05.156 --> 01:03:06.199
- Damn it!
- Come on.

01:03:07.158 --> 01:03:08.284
That punk.

01:03:16.584 --> 01:03:17.543
Let me go!

01:03:19.003 --> 01:03:21.547
I understand that you are upset,
but you shouldn't do that here.

01:03:21.839 --> 01:03:24.592
You can be charged
with obstruction of justice.

01:03:25.468 --> 01:03:28.137
I'm sorry, Officer. I'll talk to him.

01:03:28.638 --> 01:03:29.889
- My gosh.
- I'm sorry.

01:03:30.389 --> 01:03:31.432
I'm sorry.

01:03:34.852 --> 01:03:37.271
Why are you getting all worked up?

01:03:38.856 --> 01:03:42.443
Hey, let's get Jin-a out of there first.
All right?

01:03:45.404 --> 01:03:47.240
You stay here.

01:03:48.533 --> 01:03:50.827
Gosh, he's out of his mind.

01:03:55.456 --> 01:03:56.874
Don't do it, Jun-hui--

01:04:37.415 --> 01:04:40.710
You've been through a lot of heartache
because of me.

01:04:41.127 --> 01:04:43.754
Don't worry. I'll try harder.

01:04:44.255 --> 01:04:45.965
Is there something you're not telling me?

01:04:46.048 --> 01:04:47.884
Did you have fun in Gangwon-do?

01:04:47.967 --> 01:04:49.010
You went there with Jin-a.

01:04:49.093 --> 01:04:50.720
What do you mean?

01:04:52.305 --> 01:04:56.225
- Go kill yourself!
- I'm ready to listen whatever it may be.

01:04:57.476 --> 01:04:59.103
Were you that worried about me?

01:04:59.186 --> 01:05:01.355
It doesn't matter
whether you two aren't related by blood

01:05:01.439 --> 01:05:03.316
or it's not legally wrong
for you to be together.

01:05:03.399 --> 01:05:04.567
Why does it have to be Jin-a?

01:05:04.859 --> 01:05:06.360
Because it's Jin-a.

01:05:07.111 --> 01:05:09.780
- I'm sorry, Seung-ho.
- Hey, Jin-a!

01:05:12.199 --> 01:05:13.910
I didn't know

01:05:15.036 --> 01:05:17.747
that I could be loved so much by someone.

01:05:19.415 --> 01:05:20.583
I love you

01:05:22.168 --> 01:05:23.544
with all my heart.

01:05:26.213 --> 01:05:29.425
I will love you for a long time.

01:05:33.846 --> 01:05:35.848
Subtitle translation by Kim Su-hyeon
